title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 29 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 29 2022
description:
The late-night comedy shows aren't comedy shows anymore. On long Colbert interview, AOC praises Cassidy Hutchinson, bashes Republicans for seeking pardons from Trump. Clay and Buck take a call on the Jan. 6 hearings. Is a crowded GOP primary better for Trump? Gallup data: Just 26% of Democrats are proud to be Americans.
